Read in the intersections file for a a city
../../gpsaddr/data/intersections_oakland.geojson 

read a crash file from oakland in ccrs form i.e.

crashMap/data/ccrsOakland/
ccrs2016.json  ccrs2017.json  ccrs2018.json  ccrs2019.json  ccrs2020.json  ccrs2021.json  ccrs2022.json  ccrs2023.json  ccrs2024.json  ccrs2025.json

for each crash
if it has lat long, no change
if no gps

search for an intersection that matches the location
e,g,
"CollisionId": 4398060,
"PrimaryRoad": "E 12TH ST",
"SecondaryRoad": "34TH AV",

